StructureDefinition-CareConnect-Patient-1

The patient resource represents the patient involved in the provision of healthcare related services.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

This FHIR profile has no mandatory elements.

Examples

  • CareConnect-Patient-1 Example
